# =============================================================================
# Personal OS API — Jenkins Secret File
# Credential ID: env-personal-os-api-dev | env-personal-os-api-staging | env-personal-os-api-prod
#
# Canonical template: backend/.env.prod (copy that file, replace CHANGE_ME_* secrets)
#
# Values with spaces MUST be quoted, e.g. APP_DESCRIPTION="Personal OS API"
# Jenkins deploy reads POSTGRES_* via grep (does not shell-source the file).
# Used by Jenkinsfile for:
#   • personal-os-api-app-{env}  (--env-file)
#   • personal-os-pg-{env}       (POSTGRES_DATABASE_* at deploy)
# =============================================================================
